.cs 3 on
.item 'SHOW TERMINAL Command' 'Updated on 04/25/83 by EAB'
.boxon
SHOW TERMINAL [collect-options]
.*            <--------------->
.* FIELD COMMAND HELP SHOW TERMINAL collect-options
.boxoff

.* DESCRIPTION
The SHOW TERMINAL command displays the currently set terminal dependent
options.  Type HELP SET TERMINAL for a description of these options.

.* SELECT 'SHOW TERMINAL Command Options'
.us Option Descriptions

.* OPTION COLLECT-OPTIONS,BY,KEEP,NOCLEAR,NOCLR,CLEAR,CLR,WARN,NOWARN
.optix collect-options
collect-options\allow you to insert the system response to the SHOW TERMINAL
                command into your active file.  Type HELP COLLECT-OPTIONS for
                a description of these options.
.cs 3 off
